## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a3860-103">在下列的類型程式庫，`OLE_COLOR`別名`int`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a3860-103">In the following type library,  `OLE_COLOR` is an alias for `int`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a3860-104">在匯入時的引數`Color`存取子會標記為<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComAliasNameAttribute>表示該型別程式庫參考其稱為`OLE_COLOR`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a3860-104">During import, the arguments of the `Color` accessor are marked with the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComAliasNameAttribute> to indicate that type library refers to them as `OLE_COLOR`.</span></span>  
  
